G4S Security of Botswana's Full-Year Profit Rises 71% After Property Sale

-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 
2011-02-25T06:54:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/g4s-security-of-botswana-s-full-year-profit-rises-71-after-property-sale.html
G4S Security Services Botswana Ltd.
said full-year after-tax profit rose to 41 million pula compared
with 24 million pula a year earlier, boosted by the sale of its
head-office property.  The company made 15.9 million pula from the property and
lease-back agreement, Gaborone-based G4S said in a statement
published in Botswana Guardian today. It declared a 4.59 pula
per share dividend.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
 jbungu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  